</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Close the top cover. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Make sure the magnet [B] touches the bracket [C]. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-32E1E9CD-0876-47D0-A54B-5817894D4540" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-738EC6FD-D52F-44D0-9A3E-EA80C5C73604-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-738EC6FD-D52F-44D0-9A3E-EA80C5C73604-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Push the interlock assembly [C] upwards till the bracket [D] touches the stop surface [E]. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Lock the interlock assembly with the 2 screws. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-7DC84F37-C12A-4E27-8588-BC4DAEF277A8" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1F8A8174-857B-48E9-967D-58C68CB71636-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1F8A8174-857B-48E9-967D-58C68CB71636-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Make sure the bracket [D] is in the middle of the sensor assemble. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-EB55D90B-C1BD-46F0-B3F0-7CE3DFEFDC0A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D9872F47-BBE3-4A2F-B4B2-5E57F9D21C2C-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D9872F47-BBE3-4A2F-B4B2-5E57F9D21C2C-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-52B75877-A143-4BF5-96EE-CE5A84E57D22" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-09A0AB11-3BB5-4283-8325-BADEAFF646D6-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-09A0AB11-3BB5-4283-8325-BADEAFF646D6-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
